    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been loved and well-taken care of, you\u2019ve found it! This car has served me so well and is still in great shape for all your upcoming adventures. It runs smoothly and looks fantastic inside and out. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for a new home! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show you around your potential new car!",
