    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine. At its heart is the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal variable valve timing. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN variable M-differential. The chassis is sorted, featuring essential rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry with poly-bushes for sharpened turn-in. While the exterior displays honest wear reflective of its age, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. This is a high-performance specimen ready for the canyon or the track, priced to move for a discerning enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity over a concours finish.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Runs well. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
