      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The drivetrain features a precise 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, offering a visceral connection to the tarmac. This is a driver-focused machine with sorted mechanicals, ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
